{"word":"κόπος","slug":"κόπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰόπος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κόπτω\">κόπτω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘experience of distress’, <b>trouble, harassment <a href='B:470 26:10'>Mt 26:10</a>; <a href='B:480 14:6'>Mk 14:6</a>; <a href='B:490 11:7'>Lk 11:7</a>; <a href='B:490 18:5'>18:5</a>; <a href='B:540 11:23'>2 Cor 11:23</a>; <a href='B:550 6:17'>Gal 6:17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘engagement in fatiguing activity’, <b>labor, hard work <a href='B:500 4:38'>J 4:38</a></b> (in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense of ‘production’); <b><a href='B:530 3:8'>1 Cor 3:8</a>; <a href='B:530 15:58'>15:58</a>; <a href='B:540 10:15'>2 Cor 10:15</a>; <a href='B:540 11:27'>11:27</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <b><a href='B:600 3:8'>2 Th 3:8</a></b>); <b><a href='B:590 1:3'>1 Th 1:3</a>; <a href='B:590 3:5'>3:5</a>; <a href='B:730 2:2'>Rv 2:2</a>; <a href='B:730 14:13'>14:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κοπιάω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κοπρία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}